      *        拡張漢字対応
               INITIALIZE                  ORCSKANACHK2AREA
               MOVE    "2"                 TO  KANACHK2-SYORI
               MOVE    PATLSTREQ-NAME      TO  KANACHK2-MAE-INPUT
